des: Too lazy to pull out a device to check which food locations are open on campus? Well MU Dining's got you! MU Dining tells you which food locations are open on campus, so now you never have to worry about getting somewhere, just to find out that it's already closed!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
